def has_switch(remote_control:item):
    # Determine whether the remote control has a switch
    symbol has_switch=exists sw:item: is_remote_control(remote_control) and has_switch(sw)
    return has_switch

behavior turn_on_tv_with_remote_control(remote_control:item, television:item):
    body:
        achieve_once inhand(remote_control)

        if has_switch(remote_control):
            bind sw: item where:
                has_switch(sw) and close(sw, remote_control)
            achieve is_on(television)

        achieve_once is_off(remote_control)
        # Ensure the remote control is no longer in hand after turning on the TV
